Great, thank you. One more thing, could you please confirm the last four digits of the phone number we have on file for your account?

I'm not entirely sure. Let me check. Oh, it should be three one four zero.

That's great to hear. I'll think about it and maybe give you a call back if I decide on any changes.

Absolutely, take your time, Nancy. Thank you for reaching out and have a wonderful day!
